The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) National Organizing committee for the 2022 presidential primaries said accreditation for the convention will start by 6 am on Saturday. But at about 8 am this morning, journalists and other stakeholders who besieged the party headquarters at Wuse Zone Five were still waiting for accreditation. JUST IN: Hayatu-Deen pulls out PDP Presidential race as Atiku, Wike, others lock horns Children parliament tasks Jigawa govt on out-of-school children The National Working Committee (NWC) of the party were said to be locked in a meeting at the time of writing this report. The officials on the ground have refused to speak on the real situation of things.